⚔️SOLD⚔️❤️Hi friends! I’m selling my original Two Watchers painting from the LIVING AND DARK UNDEAD zine I did with @heartbeasttattoos and  @seventh_church_ministries back in 2015! ⚔️ ❤️ In case you missed it back then, this was a zine where Michelle and I reimagined LOTR characters and painted them for a zine that was so so so special to me. It was my first real art show, thanks to @jeremyhush and @illustro_obscurum - and it was also how I met a ton of incredible artists from that community who became friends and mentors to me. I won’t bore you with too much sappy stuff but I love this zine, love my Philly artist friends, and hope someone will want this painting that was part of a really amazing time in my life in their home. If you’re interested in checking it out, head over to the @unkindnessart webstore - and to see a little bit of the zine, watch the video in the next slide!

❤️ Hey friends- just wanted to pop on and let everyone know that after four fabulous years with the @unkindnessart crew I'm moving shops ❤️
I really can’t stress enough how wonderful  for me it has been working with all of the creative, talented, and extremely driven artists at Unkindness. While I am truly sad to be saying goodbye, I'm happy to announce that starting mid June I'm going to be tattooing with my good friends over at @richmondtattooclub, just a stone’s throw away! 

Over the last couple of years I’ve been busting my butt to grow as an illustrator, and this change will allow me to continue to maintain a healthy balance in my life around both my tattooing and illustration work. I cannot wait to share some of the exciting projects I’ve been working on with you. 🖤

I want to thank @teresasharpeart for mentoring me in so many ways, and ALL my friends at Unkindness, for giving me a safe place to learn and grow as an artist for the last four years. Entering the tattoo world turned my life upside down from day one, and Unkindness gave me a sense of home in that world that I desperately wanted and will never take for granted. I love you guys! ⚔️❤️
